When Julie gets to visit, she'll take the waffle makers back to your
house. That was the plan...
I was afraid snow would keep people from driving to Santa Fe from
Colorado (Raton Pass, on I-25, is closed sometimes), but it was snow
in London that kept Julie Daniel from being there. Her plane couldn't
leave.

Sandra

messages.messageBody:
That looks like fun and those look like very cool waffles. I like waffles, do you like waffles?

How very sweet to know that even though I wasn't there, I was thought of and there in people's minds.

Very sweet.

Syrupy, possibly.

Schuyler

messages.msgSnippet: Margaux associates Schuyler and family with waffles too!  At the last conference, we met their family in town and we went to a waffle bar sidewalk window and
messages.messageBody:
Margaux associates Schuyler and family with waffles too!  At the last conference, we met their family in town and we went to a waffle bar sidewalk window and Margaux, of course, got the chocolate dipped waffle which she STILL remembers. 
 
Just the other day, I was talking about their family and Margaux, a couple of hours later asked me to make her waffles!  AND that same day waffles came up in conversation WITH Schuyler!
 
Schuyler most definitely needs those delightful waffle makers!
